  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a wok or large skillet over high heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until it starts to caramelize.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the chow fun noodles and stir to combine with the onion and garlic.",
    "Add the oyster sauce, soy sauce, and sugar, and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in the sesame oil.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
